devdoc.details: Contract for managing blocklisted/paused wallets to prevent bad actors from transferring native coins

addToBlocklist(address,string).details: Add a wallet to the blocklist

addToBlocklistBatch(address[],string[]).details: Add multiple wallets to the blocklist in batch

params.reasons: Array of reasons for blocklisting (must match wallets length)

getBlocklistCount().details: Get the total number of blocklisted addresses

getBlocklistInfo(address).details: Get blocklist information for a wallet

returns.isBlocked: True if the wallet is blocklisted

initialize().details: Constructor - automatically sets the hardcoded admin address

isBlocklisted(address).details: Check if a wallet is blocklisted

returns._0: bool True if the wallet is blocklisted

removeFromBlocklist(address).details: Remove a wallet from the blocklist

params.wallet: The address to remove from blocklist

removeFromBlocklistBatch(address[]).details: Remove multiple wallets from the blocklist in batch

params.wallets: Array of addresses to remove from blocklist
